OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRalph Lauren apologises    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fover 'cultural             
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fappropriation'             
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ralph Lauren has apologised for selling
OL,6, an item which allegedly copied Mexican 
OL,7, indigenous designs.                    
OL,9,FThe US fashion chain was accused of    
OL,10,F"plagiarism" by the wife of the        
OL,11,Fcountry's president, Beatriz Gutierrez,
OL,12,Fas well as a culture minister.         
OL,14,FMexico has aimed similar complaints at 
OL,15,Fother big brands in recent years.      
OL,17,FRalph Lauren said it was "surprised" to
OL,18,Fsee the garment in question still on   
OL,19,Fsale, having issued a "stern directive"
OL,20,Fmonths previously to remove it.        
